# Cursor Rules for Joy SRS Project

## Project Overview
This is a legal strategy infographics platform for Joy Mila Enterprises, built with FastAPI and modern web technologies.

## UI Design Requirements

### Design Philosophy
- **Clarity:** Interface must be immediately understandable with clear visual hierarchy
- **Professionalism:** Modern, clean, and serious aesthetic reflecting strategic content
- **Focus:** Dark theme reduces visual noise and eye strain, making key data stand out

### Color Palette (MANDATORY)
- **Primary Brand Green:** `#41824A` - Use for buttons, active states, highlights, key conclusions
- **Accent Blue:** `#2A4B7C` - Use for main titles and gradient effects
- **Base Background:** `#1E293B` (slate-800) - Main background for all pages
- **Surface Background:** `#334155` (slate-700) - Content containers and cards
- **Text Colors:** 
  - Headings: `#F1F5F9` (slate-100)
  - Body: `#94A3B8` (slate-400)
  - Labels: `#94A3B8` (slate-300)
- **Borders:** `#475569` (slate-600)
- **Semantic Colors:**
  - Success/Low Risk: `#22C55E` (green-500)
  - Warning/Medium Risk: `#FBBF24` (amber-400)
  - Error/High Risk: `#F87171` (red-400)

### Typography
- **Font Family:** Inter (from Google Fonts)
- **Weights:** 400 (normal), 600 (semibold), 700 (bold), 800 (extrabold)
- **Scale:**
  - Hero Title: `text-4xl` to `text-6xl`, `font-extrabold`, `text-slate-100`
  - Section Title: `text-3xl` to `text-4xl`, `font-bold`, `gradient-text`
  - Card Title: `text-xl` to `text-2xl`, `font-bold`, `text-slate-100`
  - Body: `text-base` or `text-lg`, `font-normal`, `text-slate-400`
  - Labels: `text-sm`, `font-medium`, `text-slate-300`

### Layout & Spacing
- **Base Unit:** 4px (all spacing multiples of this)
- **Standard Gaps:** `gap-4` (16px), `gap-6` (24px), `gap-8` (32px)
- **Card Padding:** `p-6` (24px) or `p-8` (32px)
- **Container Width:** `max-w-7xl` with `mx-auto`

### Core Components

#### Buttons
- **Primary Action:** `bg-[#41824A]`, `text-white`, `font-semibold`, hover: `bg-green-500`, `scale-105`
- **Tabs Active:** `bg-[#41824A]`, `text-white`, `font-bold`
- **Tabs Inactive:** Transparent background, `text-gray-300`, `font-bold`, hover: `bg-slate-700`

#### Form Inputs
- **Background:** `bg-slate-700/50`
- **Text:** `text-white`
- **Placeholder:** `placeholder-gray-400`
- **Border:** `border-slate-600`
- **Focus:** `ring-2`, `ring-[#41824A]`, `border-[#41824A]`

#### Cards & Surfaces
- **Background:** `bg-slate-800` or `bg-slate-800/20` (glassmorphism)
- **Border:** `border-slate-700` or `border-white/10`
- **Rounding:** `rounded-2xl` (large), `rounded-xl` (small)
- **Shadow:** `shadow-xl` or `shadow-2xl`

### Accessibility Requirements
- **Contrast:** All text must meet WCAG AA contrast ratios
- **Semantics:** Use proper semantic HTML (`<nav>`, `<main>`, `<button>`, etc.)
- **Focus States:** All interactive elements must have visible focus states
- **Labels:** All form inputs must have associated `<label>` elements

## Technical Requirements

### Authentication
- Use JWT tokens for authentication
- Store username in localStorage for user menu display
- Implement role-based access (lawyer vs normal user)
- User menu should show login name and appropriate options

### File Structure
- All documentation goes in `docs/` folder
- Static files in `public/` folder
- Follow the established FastAPI structure

### Code Style
- Use Poetry for dependency management
- Follow PEP 8 for Python code
- Use TypeScript-like type hints
- Prefer bash/WSL/Linux shells over PowerShell

## Brand Identity
- **Company:** Joy Mila Enterprises (Pty) Ltd
- **Logo:** Use `logo.jpg` from public folder
- **Professional legal services aesthetic**
- **Strategic, authoritative tone in all content**

## Documentation
- All AI-generated documentation must be numbered and placed in `docs/` folder
- Track progress of codebase evolution through numbered documentation
- Maintain comprehensive deployment and setup guides
